clearOwnership.comment:
According to https://www.unicef.org/evaluation/media/946/file/Primero.pdf
"Ownership of Primero remains fluid based on
the humanitarian context and stability of the
government. Given the United Nations
mandate to ensure the protection of the rights
of children, in situations when governments are
not able or willing to ensure this, the ownership
of Primero has often come under UNICEF."
